Functional Requirements:
-a Referring Physician should be able to place an order into the system to allow a patient to go and get imaging by the selected modality 
that is listed in the system. 
-a Referring Physician should be able to track the patients progress to ensure the patient is properly imaged.
-a Radiologist should be able to access the work order from the referring physicians 

Non-Funtional Requirements:
-A session time out needs to be put in place in case the system is left idle more then 2 minutes. 
